@NODE "Modemtrek"
@NEXT "Wars"
@PREV "Progress"
@TOC "Main"
Name: ModemTrek
Type: Game
Info: Following up on the fairly successful @{"Solotrek" LINK "Solotrek"} is the modem
version.  The graphics have been improved considerably and the command
system has been streamlined.  The game will link over the modem to allow
players to go head to head.

This game will probably be shareware.

@ENDNODE

@NODE "Wars"
@NEXT "Babcom"
@PREV "Modemtrek"
@TOC "Main"
Name: Modem Wars
Type: Game
Info: Based on the Commodore 64 game of the same name by Electronic Arts,
Modem Wars pits you against another player in a game of war.  Multiple
terrains, multiple vehicles and optional speech synthesis make Modem
Wars a blast!

This game will be shareware.

@ENDNODE

@NODE "Babcom"
@NEXT "BJII"
@PREV "Wars"
@TOC "Main"
Name: BabCom 5
Type: Utility
Info: I recently acquired the entire episode list and info on them for the
Babylon 5 series.  The program is complete.  I am just formatting the text
for display.

This utility will be freeware.

@ENDNODE

@NODE "BJII"
@NEXT "Movie"
@PREV "Babcom"
@TOC "Main"
Name: Blackjack II
Type: Game
Info: I hate AGA!  Well, not really, but I wish I could play Klondike
Solitaire.  With that in mind, I've created Blackjack II.  It has two
decks to choose from at this point: Sports Illustrated and Playboy.
There may be a modem option.

This game will be freeware.

@ENDNODE

@NODE "Movie"
@NEXT "Map"
@PREV "BJII"
@TOC "Main"
Name: Movie Database
Type: Utility
Info: At present, I have over 200 movies on tape.  YOU try to find one in
a hurry.  The Movie Database will actually be customizable for any type
of information.

This utility will be freeware.

@ENDNODE

@NODE "Map"
@NEXT "Wincom"
@PREV "Movie"
@TOC "Main"
Name: Map Manager
Type: Utility
Info: This utility will allow the creation and display of tile maps.  I'll
be using it for dungeons and such.

This utility will be freeware.

@ENDNODE

@NODE "Wincom"
@NEXT "Sub"
@PREV "Map"
@TOC "Main"
Name: Winky Commander
Type: Game
Info: It's been a long time coming, but Winky Commander will soon be
released.  It will use rendered objects and cool digital sounds.

This game will be shareware.

@ENDNODE

@NODE "Sub"
@NEXT "Overlord"
@PREV "Wincom"
@TOC "Main"
Name: Sub Battle
Type: Game
Info: Yet another modem game!  This time, jump into your trusty sub and
enter a 3D world of torpedoes and depth charges.

This game will be freeware.

@ENDNODE

@NODE "Overlord"
@NEXT "Luncon"
@PREV "Sub"
@TOC "Main"
Name: Overlord II
Type: Game
Info: If you've seen Overlord, this will be no surprise.  But it will
have an over the modem option.

This game will be freeware.

@ENDNODE

@NODE "Luncon"
@NEXT "Mortal"
@PREV "Overlord"
@TOC "Main"
Name: Lunar Conquest 2.0
Type: Online Game
Info: With full ANSI graphic and color support, the new version of Lunar
Conquest is sure to be a big seller!

This game is shareware.

@ENDNODE

@NODE "Mortal"
@NEXT "Order"
@PREV "Luncon"
@TOC "Main"
Name: Mortal Midgets
Type: Game
Info: Teeny tiny sprites and big blobs of blood!

